  mangleData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f32c87a04b203cdf91c783d6d848f96, type: 2}
  minigame:
    cryingChild: {fileID: 1361201996}
    mysteriousWoman: {fileID: 1723158889}
    canvas: {fileID: 1424866289}
    dialog: {fileID: 1164931747}
    dialogVector:
    - {x: 0, y: 100}
    - {x: 400, y: 100}
    dialogTime: 0.35
    fade: {fileID: 1404258408}
  dialogues:
    Portuguese:
    - Ei, me escute...
    - "Sozinho voc\xEA n\xE3o pode alcan\xE7ar tudo o que quer. "
    - "Uma hora ou outra isso te leva para o decl\xEDnio."
    - "Essa \xE9 a coisa mais linda dentro de voc\xEA."
    Japanese:
    - "\u306D\u3048\u3001\u805E\u3044\u3066\u2026"
    - "\u4E00\u4EBA\u3067\u671B\u3080\u3059\u3079\u3066\u3092\u9054\u6210\u3059\u308B\u3053\u3068\u306F\u3067\u304D\u305A\u3001"
    - "\u3044\u305A\u308C\u306F\u8870\u9000\u3078\u3068\u3064\u306A\u304C\u308A\u307E\u3059\u3002"
    - "\u305D\u308C\u306F\u3042\u306A\u305F\u306E\u4E2D\u306B\u3042\u308B\u6700\u3082\u7F8E\u3057\u3044\u3082\u306E\u3067\u3059\u3002"
    English:
    - Hey, look...
    - You cannot achieve everything you want on your own.
    - Sooner or later, this will ruin you.
    - That's the most beautiful part of you.
